name: Sleepy Baby Music
description:
Sleepy Baby Music

Features:

Soothing Classical Music to fall asleep to.
Looping feature that plays the music indefinitely over and over
Classic and famous selections of legendary soothing music.

2. Sonata in G Minor No.3, Op 50, 'Didone Abbandonata' - I. Introduzione

3. 'Arabesca' from 12 Danzas Españolas [Op. 5] ,Enrique Granados i Campiña

4. Beethoven - 02 Quartet No. 10 in Eb, Op. 74- Adagio ma non troppo
